  %% Diagram 78: Unit Economics and Break-Even Trajectory Model Flow

  Input[Monthly inputs\nrevenue, burn, CAC, LTV, gross margin]
  Compute[Compute net position\nrevenue - cost]
  Trend[Compute moving trajectory to break-even]
  BE{Break-even on track for Month 16-18?}

  OnTrack[Continue planned execution]
  Report[Publish finance and investor-ready dashboard]

  OffTrack[Trajectory drift detected]
  Mitigate[Mitigation plan\nreduce burn, improve conversion, pricing adjustments]
  Reforecast[Reforecast next milestone window]

  Input --> Compute --> Trend --> BE
  BE -- Yes --> OnTrack --> Report
  BE -- No --> OffTrack --> Mitigate --> Reforecast --> Report
